text.tspan: In the XAMPP control panel, move to the Manage Servers tab located at the top portion. In the
Manage Servers tab, press the MySQL Database and click the Start button. Ensure that the status of
MySQL is green. Ask a mentor for help if it is yellow or red.
Open the terminal in your computer. Use the search function at the top right corner of your computer
if you don't know where the terminal is located.
